Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:19.23,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rome, Italy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:22.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you call this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:28.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to eat spaghetti\Nwith ink in it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:31.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well sir, this is\Nspaghetti al nero di seppia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:35.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is made with fresh squid ink,\Nso it is black.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:36.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite tasty, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:51.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! Well isn't this a treat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:55.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I like it! It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:01:00.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This hotel is going to the dogs.\NThey'll let anyone in these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:05.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Signorina, this is a gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:07.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:11.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My pretty thing, when you remove this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:14.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nat night before bed, please think of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:20.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Did that stuck-up snob\Nreally just say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:23.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's sweet enough to make\Nmy teeth hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:25.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put a spell on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:28.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Make her fall to my love charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:32.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand guys like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:38.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your magic to her lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:43.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That insinuating little dog!\NI see his game!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:45.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a travesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:46.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:52.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A little Hamon prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:56.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,These will wrap around his \Nface and stick for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He used Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:20.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, you have a call from a\NMr. Speedwagon, Mr. Caesar Zeppeli.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mamma mia! I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:30.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That skirt-chasing Casanova\Nis the Zeppeli we're here to meet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:47.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the silent depths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:53.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The pillars awaken from ages-long sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:03:01.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:08.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Summons the valorous to stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:16.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If inherited love is called fate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:22.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then take another step with smiling eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:29.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mystify the darkness, dodge in a blink
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:32.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid the blade,\Nfind an opening and strike
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:38.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Conviction tested\Nopens the way to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:43.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like a bloody storm\NHot like a bloody stone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:47.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny written into your veins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:53.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The undying bonds of honor arise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:58.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take hold of them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:07.35,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 14: Elite Ancient Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:14.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Speedwagon Foundation, founded 28
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:16.34,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Speedwagon Foundation's\NWashington headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nyears ago through Speedwagon's fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:22.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It furthers science, medicine,\Narchaeology and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:25.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...for the benefit of all humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it has a deeper purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:34.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To find the secrets of the stone masks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're using UV lights.\NPut on your masks, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce the snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The snake was absorbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:58.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Santviento isn't dead!\NHe's defending himself somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'll awaken in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:04.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! How can we kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:09.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He feeds on masked vampires,\Nand he's immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But be at ease, Mr. Speedwagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:18.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he's under these UV lights,\Nhe won't be able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:24.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:27.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take our time\Nand research a way to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:34.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These were taken in the cave where\Nwe found Santviento.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Their horns are all different!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:45.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If the one on the bottom is Santviento,\Nwho are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:52.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,According to von Stroheim, the Germans\Nfound another Pillar in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:58.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They are in a vertical line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:02.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That could indicate the ranks\Nof the Pillar Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:09.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Von Stroheim told us to meet a man in\NRome, so JoJo and I are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:18.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...is the grandson of Will A. Zeppeli,\NCaesar Zeppeli!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:24.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I take a photo of you\Nwith the fountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:31.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The birds in this country\Nsure are friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can't say I like the men, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:40.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now! You've been introduced,\Nso why can't you be civil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:45.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to be frank, Mr. Speedwagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:50.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My grandfather died tragically\Nfifty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My father took up his torch\Nand hunted the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:59.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We Italians have the strongest\Nfamily bonds in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:03.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We are proud of tradition.\NI am no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But what about that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:11.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You say he knew nothing of his\Ngrandfather until recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Such irresponsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd watch what I say, if--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I kept everything a secret from JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:29.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He fought Straizo and\None of the Pillar Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:34.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I wondered how tough he was\Nand waited for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:39.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I saw what he could do with Hamon\Nand was disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His Hamon is simply not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:47.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His victory against the Pillar Man\Nwas blind luck for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:50.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will never work with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:54.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar, he hasn't trained with Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:03.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you with a good thrashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:04.38,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:09.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With your Hamon, you couldn't\Neven beat this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then you couldn't even beat a pigeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:26.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I love to make fun,\Nbut I won't be made fun of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:35.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He gave this girl a Hamon kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:41.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't even beat this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Should I stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:48.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, even if it's hard on him,\Nif he can't get through this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:01.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My grandfather only died because\Nyour grandfather got in his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept someone of\Nyour bloodline!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar, that's too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:16.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't leave it at just me,\Nyou had to insult my dead grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:21.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a technique\Nsure to eliminate the Pillar Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:27.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My Hamon Bubble Launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:34.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My gloves and clothing are coated\Nin a special soap mixture!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:38.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blast you back home, Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:57.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you're still conscious,\Nbut your Hamon won't break you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:10:00.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And look at that,\Nyour breathing is ragged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:07.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now you'll say, Signorina,\NI will lift my Hamon spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:12.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here, signorina,\NI will lift my Hamon spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:29.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I put a Hamon-filled pigeon in her mouth\Nwhile I was being choked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:34.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd kiss her again\Nto remove your Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:40.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't even beat a pigeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:58.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who does this jerk think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:01.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have to grandstand\Njust to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He really ticks me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:10.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I had a technique like his Bubble\NLauncher, he wouldn't be so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to come up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:17.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But working at it would be a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:21.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show him what's what\Nwith a card game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to, JoJo?\NDeal the cards normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:27.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to deal normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa-oa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I've been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:44.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't beat me without\Nresorting to sly gimmicks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:48.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what is this mirror\Non your shoe for, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You want a piece of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it, rube!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been eight hours.\NWhat are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What am I waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:04.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:11.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?! A German soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Germans guard the Pillar Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'll get us in to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:23.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Germany and Italy have an alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:48.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the Germans want to do\Nscientific research on my Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:52.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're Englishmen, but\Nyou're allowed to see the Pillar Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:58.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can thank my\Npainstaking efforts for that, JoJo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Speedwagon, we have\Nmany questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:05.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together\Nto stop them before they wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How is your girlfriend back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:19.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm going home\Nto get married next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:20.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mamma mia! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was his wingman when\Nhe picked her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, keep your eyes on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop nuzzling the wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:45.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No girl would want to\Ndate a guy like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It would be easier to find Nessie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:53.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This guy really thinks he's hot stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:58.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come up with a killer technique\Nand teach him a thing or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Something's strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:13.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! They're under UV lights!\NThey can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take care and look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The death of von Stroheim's team\Nwas an important lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:28.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have to cut the Pillar out and\Nput it in a bunker in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:33.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?\NThere's a shadow, so I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I hear something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He couldn't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out more UV lamps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:54.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:09.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's blocking the UV light\Nwith blood and brain matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:30.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The world has changed while I slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:34.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can see how\Nin these paltry inventions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:39.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can hold me\Nwith your feeble lights?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:45.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:48.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're stuck together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:16.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken, my masters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:33.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The famous Mouth of Truth\Nwas a secret entrance all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This place is so unearthly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:46.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar, have you tried Hamon\Non the sleeping Pillar Men?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:51.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hamon is only useful on the living.\NIt has no effect on stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work unless they are awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:59.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are the guards that\Nare supposed to be here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one's here! It's too quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a guard posted here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I just stepped in something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:17.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the grossest feeling ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The husks of soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:38.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dutch! Don't run off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something's out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:45.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be! Th-They're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:46.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:51.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of there, Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:11.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar... Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:21.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't even notice what happened\Nwhen one of them bumped into Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:25.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's like when a man\Nsteps on an ant while walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is night outside, Wamuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:36.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lord Kars. What is your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:41.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Searching for the whereabouts\Nof the Red Stone of Aja, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:48.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is the Stone and\Nthe Mask will be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:54.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Master Esidisi, the human world\Nhas changed much over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:58.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, the Emperor of Rome\Nhad the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:02.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that age has ended, I am sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:07.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then we must find out\Nwhere the Stone has gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:11.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They say the Emperor\Ncherished the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:15.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure humans\Nstill tell stories of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall find the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:25.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let us go outside and\Nobserve the changes in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:42.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, worm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay your hand, Esidisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, Lord Kars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:53.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu, I know how you hate\Nwhen someone enters your shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:57.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot how you reflexively attack\Nanyone who does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It has been 2,000 years, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:04.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have offended you, my lord.\NPunish me as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is no reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:13.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is that very fighting spirit\Nthat lets me rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:17.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The fault is mine\Nfor entering your shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Wamuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Kars...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We go, Wamuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:34.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me! Kill me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:39.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's starting to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:45.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was numb at first, but the pain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:49.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please kill me now, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:56.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're powerless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:01.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The hopelessness is overwhelming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:06.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C-Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:33.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was just a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just an ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He loved his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:39.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And his girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And his country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:45.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was a normal,\Nhardworking young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:51.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:56.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:58.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This fight is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:03.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do this myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:38.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:41.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm tired of talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:43.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's spineless!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:46.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Hamon tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:49.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Divine Sandstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:51.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 15: A Hero's Proof
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:53.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
